HEADWORD: ixodid
<hw>ixodid</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a member of the <fam>Ixodidae</fam>,
a family of ticks having a hard shield on the back and mouth parts that
project from the head.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hard tick.</syn>⟦br⟧
